1.title: Human Dolls
1.plot: Two prominent plastic surgeons, specialize in helping patients repair, what is often deemed, irreparable. As a last resort, these people, at their most vulnerable, arrive, hoping these two doctors, can perform, what others cannot.

2.title: Janice Dickinson Knows Breast
2.plot: Supermodel Janice Dickinson's breast enhancements are from the '70s, and they need a re-do! Drs. Dubrow and Nassif take on the high-profile assignment, but difficulties arise when post-op painkillers clash with Janice's addictive past. Will her over-the-top personality endanger her recovery process? Meanwhile, new patient Paul's bungled nose job left him with a crooked septum, causing him constant migraine headaches. Can the doctors help?

3.title: Vagina Bomb!

Then, Jenn has struggled with the look of her nose thanks to one of the most twisted septums the doctors have ever seen. See if they can fix two botched surgeries and restore Jenn's self-confidence!

4.title: Making of a Belieber
4.plot: Toby is an aspiring musician who's spent more than $100,000 to look like his idol Justin Bieber. Can he convince Drs. Dubrow and Nassif to continue his transformation? Then, Charlotte is at her wits' end after a botched breast augmentation has left her saggy and wrinkly. Dr. Dubrow has a plan to reconstruct her chest in time for Charlotte's sister-in-law's wedding. Plus, Desiree's budget tummy tuck in Tijuana was a nightmare that pulled her privates up to her belly button. See if the doctors can restore her midriff and her confidence!

Next, Diana's rhinoplasty 10 years ago resulted in a pig-ish looking nose and she's finally fulfilling her dream of having Dr. Nassif fix it. Then, Dr. Dubrow learns to vogue in an unforgettable consultation with one of the world's foremost Madonna impersonators. Meet the fabulous Venus Delight!

6.title: Boob Freak!

Then, Mike suffers from a nasty head scar, but can't be operated on until his skin stretches. So doctors devise a bold idea! Plus, see if the doctors can fix Michelle's cleft chin mishap.

7.title: Girls Gone Wildd

Meanwhile, Salina's breasts are a mess after two botched boob jobs in a row, but it's what she's not telling the doctors that could ruin her repair. Then, Cristina's tummy tuck went very wrong, leaving the single mother of 3 with terrible scarring and a flesh-eating infection. 8.title: Silicone Valley
8.plot: International singing sensation Monique's myriad of plastic surgeries have left her ears pulled down to her jawline. Can Drs. Dubrow and Nassif get her ear lobes fixed in time for her next music video shoot? Meanwhile, Kelly's childhood surgeries left her with a crooked nose and uneven lip. See if the corrective surgery finally gives her the confidence to take wedding photos she skipped years ago. Plus, Myesha's quest to be a model was halted by a cheap surgery that caused the bags under her eyes to swell. Watch her get back on track!

Maria Menounos hosts as Monique Allen, Michelle Blackwell and Desiree White answer questions about their plastic surgery horror stories. Plus, Janice Dickinson returns to have one last procedure right on stage! Then, stick around for a first look at season two!
